<br>
If alone, sense/disarm it, and move through. If you're disarming for a raid/group, sense once, then keep it disarmed continually until everyone has moved through the area.<br>
<br>
To disarm the trap heading toward the royals, creep out an inch or two past the middle of the bridge to sense it. To disarm it from the other side, make sure you do it a slight distance back from the door, or you can trigger it. Just be aware and it won't pose a problem. :)<br>
